Eva Longoria, 47, showed off her phenomenal figure on Instagram at the weekend as she shared an exercise video. The Desperate Housewives star could be seen working out with dumbbells looking into the mirror while her camera videoed her from behind. She wore bright pink leggings and a matching small exercise top for the grilling routine. Eva showed off her peachy rear as she did a number of squats, showing how she keeps her figure in top shape. The actress kept the pink theme going this weekend as she was spotted in Hollywood wearing fuschia shorts and a matching blazer.